metadata.title: Buckle-Down Men's Standard Canvas Bifold Wallet Paisley Skulls, 4.0" x 3.5"
features: Carry your cash and cards in style with Buckle-Down's bi-fold wallet.
This men's bi-fold wallet is made from high-density woven canvas.
It measures 4.0"x3.5"x0.5", and features the standard billfold, 5 card slots, and windowed ID holder.
All artwork is applied using advanced printing technologies, so the wallet will still look good after years of hard use.
This product is handcrafted in the USA by Buckle-Down, Inc. and is Officially Licensed by Buckle-Down, Inc.
